messages.message:
<!here> We will be removing py2 from our codebase over the next few weeks, since the Oct 21 release was the last release to support Py2. Any py2 changes will be cherry-picks on that branch. Going forward, our code base will be py3 only!

Thanks everyone for their hard work in this effort, especially @dlluncor for spear-heading the whole py2->py3 migration!
